casebody.data:
Wells, Respondent, v. Sibley et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. April 13, 1892.) Action by George W. Wells against Rufus A. Sibley and others.

Argued before Dwight, P. J., and Macomber and Lewis, JJ.

No opinion. Motion for leave to appeal to the court of appeals granted. See 17 N. Y. Supp. 417.
